{"tid":2346891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘇文隆: 被告鬼祟踢警長 假使警長跌倒可能令人群蜂擁而至攻擊 後果不堪設想 判囚4個月","createTime":"2020-12-30T15:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T17:35:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"21afe54e80c847e5ad4cb09dd7fe8c6356bacee7","tid":2346891,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"擁有會計學歷之的士司機於今年1月5日「新春上水和你行」集會遊行期間，在上水中心樓梯位置從後向便裝警長踢了一腳，今日在粉嶺裁判法院承認一項襲警罪。主任裁判官蘇文隆指，難以估計現場示威人士的信念和傾向，被告的行為可能令人群蜂擁而至攻擊警長，後果不堪設想，判囚4個月，但批准被告保釋等候上訴。<br />\n<br />\n辯方資深大律師潘熙建議法庭判以4至6星期的短期監禁，並指被告於今年9月14日自願撤銷擔保後，已被還柙7星期零4天，其後在獄中因身體狀況欠佳，再度申請保釋。被告擁有會計學士學歷，志願投考公務員，但案發後已感到機會渺茫。被告考獲的士牌，現時任職的士司機。被告已計劃移民澳洲重投會計行業，下月亦將往面試，開展人生規劃的另一步。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">蘇官指縱使被告出腳時現場情況相對和平，而出腳亦不見得大力，警長也沒有受傷，並且即時回頭迅速制服被告；但被告從後施襲，行為鬼祟，有機會令警長跌倒。加上被告承認的案情顯示現場早前混亂，假使警長跌倒，當時2樓仍有不少人，無人掌握他們的信念及傾向，有可能蜂擁而至攻擊警長，後果不堪設想，因此以6個月監禁為量刑起點，鑑於被告認罪，判囚4個月。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/LBCZWFR7RVDE7BHOM4P6KN65EQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FLBCZWFR7RVDE7BHOM4P6KN65EQ%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSCNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=83913255\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FLBCZWFR7RVDE7BHOM4P6KN65EQ%2F&h=d219bb53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/LBCZWFR7RVDE7BHOM4P6KN65EQ/</a>"},{"pid":"7ebab1065d5ce0930a242cd1f14fbd5941b2e272","tid":2346891,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bc1040586e7009629244962ac0a7822ad4bbe4","tid":2346891,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d71f181df7eac271a08d9901a1e6f31acde12b","tid":2346891,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cb5ea54a66fc0ccaa1f16e6ddc915a44dff42b","tid":2346891,"uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"屌，判咁撚重既"},{"pid":"f432a0055c20592c5699bc6afdea804dde05b745","tid":2346891,"uid":225130,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:05:53.000Z","msg":"可能可能<br />\n<br />\n有罪推家定"},{"pid":"f129cb34fa7cb03ca6a608cb48184f50fb12317a","tid":2346891,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5cb5ea54a66fc0ccaa1f16e6ddc915a44dff42b","tid":2346891,"uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"屌，判咁撚重既"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">辯方列出以下幾項案例：<br />\n1. 腳踢向警員的腳部，判處6星期；<br />\n2. 用腳踢警員，判處3星期；<br />\n3. 扯警員頭髮，判處3星期；<br />\n4. 推撞警員的胸部，經審訊後，判處社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n辯方繼續呈上不同案例：<br />\n1. 莊子東案例中，涉及2項襲警的控罪，包括腳踢向警員和碰撞其胸部，經過審訊後，以8個星期作量刑起點，最後判處37天。經過上訴後，改判社會服務令；<br />\n2. 2015年的黃智佳案例，因為被告本身有案底，認罪後判處6星期；<br />\n3. 朱家言的襲警案例，經上訴後判處為社會服務令。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0c47a1b0f74d45b815cff6e0d04272a5f0d0a475","tid":2346891,"uid":201604,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"做狗就預左畀人打<br />\n你估而家玩紅綠燈 跌左